Package us.dahp.spellsapi.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SpellCastEvent
    When a player casts a spell.
    SpellEvent
    Abstract class that is super event of all other spell events.
    SpellHitBlockEvent
    Called when a spell hits a block.
    SpellHitEntityEvent
    When a spell hits an entity.
    SpellLearnEvent
    When a user learns a new spell.
    SpellLevelUpEvent
    When a player levels up a spell.
    SpellPostCastEvent
    After a cast, when durability and spell cast timer taken into account.
    SpellSelectionSwitchEvent
    When a player changes their selected spell.
